title: The.Summit.2012.HDTV.XviD-spinzes.avi
description:
Full-length Documentary examining one of the most disastrous events in mountaineering history, when a team of 22 climbers tried to reach the peak of K2 in the Himalayas, but only 11 survived. The film-makers travel to the mountain in an attempt to understand the causes of the tragedy, as well as interviewing the survivors and the families of those who died.
